## Frequency Counting Patterns

```mermaid
graph LR
    Key[Key] --> Hash[Hash Function]
    Hash --> B0[Bucket 0]
    Hash --> B1[Bucket 1]
    Hash --> B2[Bucket 2]
    B1 --> N1[Node A] --> N2[Node B]
